Class CompositeDefinition.Tier

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.CompositeDefinition.Tier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject
    Enclosing class:
    CompositeDefinition

    public static class CompositeDefinition.Tier
extends AbstractXmlObject
    Tier application within a composite. Other than just indicating which apps are part of a composite, it also defines how to correlate a given link on a tier to a link on the primary tier app.
